Interface CloseableIterator<E>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AutoCloseable, Iterator<E>

    public interface CloseableIterator<E>
extends Iterator<E>, AutoCloseable
    Interface that combines Iterator and AutoCloseable. Why does Java 8 not support this natively?!?
    Author:
    mikepersonick
